      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Main models\n1. Reference Master (template)\n-> policy-term: ststic\n-> payment freq: static\n\n2. Customer \n-> cid : uuid\n-> name(req) : string\n-> age(req) : int (18-65)\n-> ph no(req): int(10digit)\n-> pan no(conditionally req) : (string)\n-> address(data): string\n-> email(data) : string\n-> gender(data) : enum\n\n3. Policy\n-> policy_id : uuid\n-> cust_id(limk while build) : uuid\n->policy name(data) : string\n-> policyTerm(req) : int\n-> policy freq(req) : int\n-> policy premium(req) : int\n-> sum(req) : int\n-> nominee{\n        name\n        relation\n        age\n    }\n-> status(auto(draft,active,completed,rejected)) : enum\n-> policynumber(global after submission) : uuid\n-> applydate: isotimestamp\n-> issuedate : isotimesatmp\n\n4. Audits\n-> auditid\n-> policy_id\n-> cust_id\n-> action\n-> module\n-> timestamp",
      "fontSize": 63,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Main models\n1. Reference Master (template)\n-> policy-term: ststic\n-> payment freq: static\n\n2. Customer \n-> cid : uuid\n-> name(req) : string\n-> age(req) : int (18-65)\n-> ph no(req): int(10digit)\n-> pan no(conditionally req) : (string)\n-> address(data): string\n-> email(data) : string\n-> gender(data) : enum\n\n3. Policy\n-> policy_id : uuid\n-> cust_id(limk while build) : uuid\n->policy name(data) : string\n-> policyTerm(req) : int\n-> policy freq(req) : int\n-> policy premium(req) : int\n-> sum(req) : int\n-> nominee{\n        name\n        relation\n        age\n    }\n-> status(auto(draft,active,completed,rejected)) : enum\n-> policynumber(global after submission) : uuid\n-> applydate: isotimestamp\n-> issuedate : isotimesatmp\n\n4. Audits\n-> auditid\n-> policy_id\n-> cust_id\n-> action\n-> module\n-> timestamp",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
